"détails</a>"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid "Architectural Excellence for Corporate Success"
msgstr ""
"L'excellence architecturale au service de la prospérité des entreprises"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Book an appointment and see how we can unlock your potential<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"Prenez rendez-vous et découvrez comment nous pouvons révéler votre potentiel."
"<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Book now"
msgstr "Réserver maintenant"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Detailed Project Management"
msgstr "Une gestion de projet détaillée"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Discover our latest collection: sustainable, innovative designs that blend "
"modern elegance with timeless architectural beauty."
msgstr ""
"Découvrez notre dernière collection : des designs durables et innovants qui "
"allient l'élégance moderne à la beauté architecturale intemporelle."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_enark.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nom d'affichage"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Embrace eco-friendly architecture with sustainable design solutions that "
"reduce environmental impact."
msgstr ""
"Adoptez une architecture respectueuse de l'environnement grâce à des "
"solutions de conception durable qui réduisent l'impact environnemental."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Experience seamless project execution with meticulous planning, budgeting, "
"and oversight from concept to completion."
msgstr ""
"Bénéficiez d'une exécution de projet parfaite grâce à une planification, une "
"budgétisation et une supervision méticuleuses, de la conception à  la "
"finalisation du projet."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_enark.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Innovative Design Solutions"
msgstr "Des solutions de conception innovantes"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_title
msgid "Innovative architecture <br/>and sustainable design solutions"
msgstr ""
"Une architecture innovante <br/>et des solutions de conception durables"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid ""
"Our architectural solutions combine design excellence with business acumen, "
"creating spaces that inspire and support your corporate goals. Transform "
"your workspace with our expertise."
msgstr ""
"Nos solutions architecturales combinent l'excellence du design et le sens "
"des affaires pour créer des espaces qui inspirent et soutiennent les "
"objectifs de votre entreprise. Transformez votre espace de travail grâce à "
"notre expertise."

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_freegrid
msgid "Start a Project"
msgstr "Lancez un projet"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_cta_box
msgid "Still hesitating ?<br/>Contact us, it's free"
msgstr "Vous hésitez encore ?<br/>Contactez-nous, c'est gratuit"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid "Sustainable Building Practices"
msgstr "Des pratiques de construction durables"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_enark.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thèmes utiles"

#. module: theme_enark
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_enark.s_features_wall
msgid ""
"Transform your vision into reality with cutting-edge architectural designs "
"tailored to your unique needs and aesthetic preferences."
msgstr ""
"Faites de votre vision une réalité grâce à des conceptions architecturales "
"ultramodernes adaptées à vos besoins uniques et à vos préférences "
"esthétiques."
